{"tid":1732970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"救理大只有一個方法","createTime":"2019-11-18T03:56:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T06:50:33.000Z","uid":168911,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"31ca0617c57ac524cb6c4a4c44bd0b684051e297","tid":1732970,"uid":168911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:56:07.000Z","msg":"就係係第二個地方搞一個更大獲<br />\n<br />\n對方重兵駐守<br />\n攻打缺口係行唔通<br />\n除非你有更高武力優勢<br />\n<br />\n唯用diversion 方法"},{"pid":"5dcb50ae88d97d4721c29f33e4ff3d047332b784","tid":1732970,"uid":168911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:59:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca6507021438b228b3481e8e7bc9dd13e3f23fcb","tid":1732970,"uid":322608,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:59:15.000Z","msg":"我係P牌，一日出唔到兩個post，可否幫我將呢個Message發俾理大手足...<br />\n<br />\n全世界都想看見你們的決心<br />\n可否你們錄一段全部人一起唱⟨⟨榮光⟩⟩及求救訊息<br />\n把影片發給全世界媒體"},{"pid":"0e282fd32238f22af6e867500de7bc259206a7e9","tid":1732970,"uid":71509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:00:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"603df71ea7e28cee7c0797644894e02eb18509a7","tid":1732970,"uid":198233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:01:04.000Z","msg":"推狗宿"},{"pid":"6a5b99cf96ef1821582248fbdba93dd08776c8b6","tid":1732970,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:04:24.000Z","msg":"入黎睇下先<br />\n<br />\n「將軍抽車」而家既情況好需要呢個物資<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1731397\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1731397</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a42115e0c163008c87d99330fe0a1ad612a3d144","tid":1732970,"uid":259963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:04:47.000Z","msg":"#手足投稿 #手足建議 <br />\n而家所有人唔應該塞曬係尖沙咀紅磡。留一批和理非係到聲援，另一批就去狗屋狗宿火攻。咁就可以引到理大現場嘅狗車調走。其他地方都要開花，以免可以支援到！<br />\n當狗車調走後會有缺口，手足就容易d係個缺口到返出黎！<br />\n根本而家係防到出面入唔到去，入面又出唔到黎。大家對恃最辛苦係入面嘅手足呀！"},{"pid":"2e4adfe7bcf500443ab38da7073cd5a5e9a0eb75","tid":1732970,"uid":316537,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:06:33.000Z","msg":"重返暴大有冇得諗"},{"pid":"2a3efd4946f479cec4a33a5a9e7d7a13074e2a0d","tid":1732970,"uid":41260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:07:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家千奇唔好</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一喺就盡地一鋪 私家車大貨車全部踩衡油剷入去開路<br />\n浴血死戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一喺就各區裝修政府建築物、狗宿狗屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢依家理大就食硬你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家唔攻應該係想引啲人過去支援 順手拉埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n與其畀佢慢慢拉 最後失理大<br />\n不如一鼓作氣 盡地一鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n救人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47253b647539ec904f460bbbf062d22124d040da","tid":1732970,"uid":326665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:13:57.000Z","msg":"Poly 入面所有手足即刻拍短片，講定遺言，例如同父母道歉，同朋友道歉同道別咁。有咁慘得咁慘，喊得勁啲。<br />\n並堅決表明寧願餓死入面都唔會出來。叫人想像下成個poly 都係屍體嘅畫面，話係政府一手造成！<br />\n<br />\n香港人受軟唔受硬，如果有大量呢啲遺言短片，我相信相幾會會感動到香港人，喚醒到更多人企出來比壓力政府"},{"pid":"7331c4b2bfa56b28bdfa40b64c6b9ae0cf2d3f0b","tid":1732970,"uid":168911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:17:34.000Z","msg":"類似諗法既post:<br />\n<br />\n圍魏救趙 全港大裝修<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1733432/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1733432/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"cf696f6545ffecdbf664d745e7f297d4086b54dc","tid":1732970,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:18:32.000Z","msg":"1400 被捕<br />\nY7055178<br />\n顏朗謙"},{"pid":"a9c83d4f5fbd443a02d319f0b31c200782933608","tid":1732970,"uid":247857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:47:58.000Z","msg":"呢個岩 去第二個地方搞更大嘅嘢"},{"pid":"de96c2da5b58ee73f86ccd5de71458310b26e34d","tid":1732970,"uid":39436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:48:38.000Z","msg":"而加要打持久戰！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1732869\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1732869</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫推pls"},{"pid":"01ba0f8ec251ad7a984258c8554f50f582cfdffd","tid":1732970,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:50:33.000Z","msg":"認真，屠殺藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}